      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive law must be justified for high-shear rotating-machinery flow; alternative model-form uncertainty quantified.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected without comparison to higher-fidelity LES or DNS reference data in the VAD regime. Power-law hemolysis model used without alternative-form uncertainty estimate. Achieved level 2 vs required level 5."
    },
