      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ campaign with 1 200 samples performed. Inlet turbulence intensity and red-cell damage exponent identified as dominant inputs in the campaign report. However, material property distributions for blood viscosity were assumed Gaussian without experimental justification. Achieved level 3 vs required level 5."
